<p class=A3Topic>Window Functions and Methods </p>



<p>Alpha Anywhere provides the following functions for controlling Alpha Anywhere
 windows.</p>




<table style="x-cell-content-align: top;
				border-left-style: None;
				border-top-style: None;
				border-right-style: None;
				border-bottom-style: None;
				border-spacing: 0px;
				border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0">
<col>
<col>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td class="tableHeader" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableHead>Function</td>
<td class="tableHeader" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableHead>Description</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_CLOSE_ALL_WINDOWS Function.xml" title="A5_CLOSE_ALL_WINDOWS Function" class="wiki">A5_CLOSE_ALL_WINDOWS(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Closes all open windows except for the <span class=Screen>Control 
 Panel</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_MDI_WINDOWclass_ADD Function.xml" title="A5_MDI_WINDOWclass_ADD Function" class="wiki">A5_MDI_WINDOWCLASS_ADD(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Creates a new minimized window of a specified class.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_ISMAXIMIZED Function.xml" title="A5_ISMAXIMIZED Function" class="wiki">A5_ISMAXIMIZED(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns .T. if the MDI child window has been maximized.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_LIST_OPEN_WINDOWS Function.xml" title="A5_LIST_OPEN_WINDOWS Function" class="wiki">A5_LIST_OPEN_WINDOWS(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns a CR-LF delimited list of open windows.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_WINDOWBAR_CLOSE Function.xml" title="A5_WINDOWBAR_CLOSE Function" class="wiki">A5_WINDOWBAR_CLOSE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Hides the <span class=Screen>Window Bar</span> at the 
 bottom of the screen.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_WINDOWBAR_IS_OPEN Function.xml" title="A5_WINDOWBAR_IS_OPEN Function" class="wiki">A5_WINDOWBAR_IS_OPEN(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Indicates whether the <span class=Screen>Window Bar</span> 
 is open.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_WINDOWBAR_SHOW Function.xml" title="A5_WINDOWBAR_SHOW Function" class="wiki">A5_WINDOWBAR_SHOW(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Shows the <span class=Screen>Window Bar</span> at the 
 bottom of the screen.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/A5_WINDOWBAR_TOGGLE Function.xml" title="A5_WINDOWBAR_TOGGLE Function" class="wiki">A5_WINDOWBAR_TOGGLE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Shows or hides the <span class=Screen>Window Bar</span> 
 at the bottom of the screen.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_ENUM Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_ENUM Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_ENUM(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Creates a CR-LF delimited character string that lists 
 the windows currently available on your system.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_GET Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_GET Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_GET(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Obtains the Window Handle of a program that is identified 
 by its <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_HIDE Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_HIDE Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_HIDE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Hides the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_MAXIMIZE Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_MAXIMIZE Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_MAXIMIZE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Maximizes the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_MINIMIZE Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_MINIMIZE Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_MINIMIZE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Minimizes the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_MOVE Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_MOVE Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_MOVE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Moves the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span> 
 to new coordinates.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_POSITION_GET Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_POSITION_GET Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_POSITION_GET(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns a character string containing the coordinates 
 of the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_RESIZE Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_RESIZE Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_RESIZE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Resizes the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span> 
 to new dimensions.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_RESTORE Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_RESTORE Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_RESTORE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Restores the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_SHOW Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_SHOW Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_SHOW(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Shows the window specified by <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Window Functions/SYS_ID_SIZE_GET Function.xml" title="SYS_ID_SIZE_GET Function" class="wiki">SYS_ID_SIZE_GET(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns a character string containing the width and 
 height in inches of <span class=Argument>Window_Name</span>.</td></tr>
</table>

<p>Alpha Anywhere provides the following methods for controlling the application 
 window.&nbsp;These methods apply to <span class=Bolded>Forms</span>, <span 
 class=Bolded>Browses</span>, and the <span class=Bolded>Status Bar</span>. 
 Refer to the method description for the proper way to call the method.</p>




<table style="x-cell-content-align: top;
				border-left-style: None;
				border-top-style: None;
				border-right-style: None;
				border-bottom-style: None;
				width: 100%;
				border-spacing: 0px;
				border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<col style="width: 150px;">
<col style="width: 654px;">

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td class="tableHeader" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableHead>Function</td>
<td class="tableHeader" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableHead>Description</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Object/OBJECT.HIDE Method.xml" title="OBJECT.HIDE Method" class="wiki">.HIDE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Hides the window.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Object/OBJECT.ISVISIBLE Method.xml" title="OBJECT.ISVISIBLE Method" class="wiki">.ISVISIBLE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns .T. (TRUE) if a window is visible; otherwise, 
 returns .F. (FALSE).</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Object/OBJECT.MAXIMIZE Method.xml" title="OBJECT.MAXIMIZE Method" class="wiki">.MAXIMIZE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Maximizes the window.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Object/OBJECT.MINIMIZE Method.xml" title="OBJECT.MINIMIZE Method" class="wiki">.MINIMIZE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Minimizes the window.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Object/OBJECT.RESTORE Method.xml" title="OBJECT.RESTORE Method" class="wiki">.RESTORE(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Restores the window to its size before a .MINIMIZE()or 
 .MAXIMIZE().</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Object/OBJECT.SHOW Method.xml" title="OBJECT.SHOW Method" class="wiki">.SHOW(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Displays the window.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Object/OBJECT.SIZE_GET Method.xml" title="OBJECT.SIZE_GET Method" class="wiki">.SIZE_GET(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns a character string containing the width and 
 height in inches of the window.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Form/FORM.WINDOW_POSITION Method.xml" title="FORM.WINDOW_POSITION Method" class="wiki">.WINDOW_POSITION(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Positions a window on the screen. Has features supported 
 only by V6.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Desktop_Api/Form/FORM.ZORDER Method.xml" title="FORM.ZORDER Method" class="wiki">.ZORDER(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Sets the z-order stacking position of a MDI child window.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Api/Objects/A5/A5.ACTIVATING Method.xml" title="A5.ACTIVATING Method" class="wiki">A5.ACTIVATING(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns the name of the MDI window that has just got 
 focus.</td></tr>

<tr style="x-cell-content-align: top;" valign="top">
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 150px;" valign="top" width="150px">
<p class=TableLeft><a href="/Api/Objects/A5/A5.DEACTIVATING Method.xml" title="A5.DEACTIVATING Method" class="wiki">A5.DEACTIVATING(</a>)</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1" class="TableCell" style="x-cell-content-align: top; width: 654px;" valign="top" width="654px">
<p class=TableLeft>Returns the name of the MDI window that has just lost 
 focus.</td></tr>
</table>

